# Keep the build context small and secrets/artifacts OUT of the image.
# Docker sends everything here to the daemon before building; ignoring these makes
# builds faster and — critically — prevents .env (your API key) from ever entering an image.
.venv/
.git/
.github/
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
data/
.chroma/
.vscode/
.DS_Store
*.log
